      "requiredLevel": 1,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2; qualitative equivalency review conducted.",
      "rationale": "Qualitative review confirms that simulation input parameters are equivalent to experimental conditions within the bounds documented in test protocol TP-CBP-2022-04. Formal equivalency analysis not required at MRL 2 per credibility plan CP-CBP-2022."
