    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required gradation levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out per the documented credibility plan CP-CBP-2022. Output comparison achieves gradation 3, exceeding the MRL 2 requirement. The CFD hemolysis model is accepted as credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device within the operating envelope defined in the assessment documentation.",
